		<RichText x="738" y="255" width="414" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷丘丘王进行勾拳、捶地2段的普通攻击，分别造成<span color="#ffacff">37.5%,40%</span><span>伤害。<br/></span><span color="#dc72ff">魔化状态：</span><span>捶地产生</span><span color="#ffbfbf">2</span><span>个电气碎石。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="421" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffdfff">(魔化)<span color="#ffffff">雷丘丘王左手伏地冲过来，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，蓄力时间可长可短。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="428" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷丘丘王侧身蓄力起跳，重重下落造成<span color="#b9b9b9">100%</span><span>伤害，并留下</span><span color="#ffbfbf">1</span><span>个电气碎石，形成碎石的落雷造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害：<br/></span><span color="#dc72ff">魔化状态：</span><span>落地产生</span><span color="#ffbfbf">3</span><span>个电气碎石。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="927" width="395" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffdfff">(魔化)<span color="#ffffff">雷丘丘王蓄力进行飞扑，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">62.5%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，可突然进行飞扑攻击。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="918" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷丘丘王从地上挖并抛出1只雷史莱姆或者变异雷史莱姆，均造成<span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害。<br/></span><span color="#dc72ff">魔化状态：<br/></span><span>1.抛出一只大雷史莱姆，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">62.5%</span><span>伤害；<br/>2.抛出一只变异大雷史莱姆，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">62.5%</span><span>伤害，其产生3个碎屑，每个造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害；</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1411" y="255" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷丘丘王进行扩胸运动，全身变雷晶发亮，进入<span color="#ff99ff">魔化状态</span><span>，并附属</span><span textDecoration="underline">雷甲</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷丘丘王进行一次勾拳，朝任意方向挥一拳，造成<span color="#ffacff">37.5%</span><span>伤害。<br/></span><span color="#dc72ff">魔化状态：</span><span>使用左手蓄力一挥，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">37.5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="703" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷丘丘王进行固定2次的双锤地攻击，两次分别造成<span color="#ffacff">50%,62.5%</span><span>伤害，第二次锤击的范围更大。<br/></span><span color="#dc72ff">魔化状态：</span><span>锤地产生</span><span color="#ffbfbf">2-3</span><span>个电气碎石。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="927" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffdfff">处于魔化状态下的<span color="#ffffff">雷丘丘王的部分技能会留下</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#ffffff">电气碎石</span><span color="#ffffff">，一段时间后爆炸，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，也可被雷丘丘王的</span><span color="#ffbfbf">冲撞</span><span color="#ffffff">引爆。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
