		<RichText x="67" y="1200" width="437" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷甲：<span color="#ffacff">18雷</span><span>盾，持续90s。该状态下，抗打断0，免疫风场力。<br/>电气碎石：</span><span color="#ffacff">3雷</span><span>盾，持续20s，具有嘲讽，可被丘丘王冲撞提前引爆。</span></p>
			</content>
